---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 3.0
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Added support for SunFire X2200M2
- Added SERD behavior modification, only report error if 24/24
  condition is met (24 errors on same DIMM within 24 hours).

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 2.0 (2009-01-23) r46025
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Replaced OpenIPMI with custom code
- Logs SEL using Request Event command (no longer uses Add SEL command)
- Correctly encodes DIMM pair information in SEL event packet
- Added -s option to run single check/report iteration
- Added support for Chip Kill ECC syndromes
- Added silkscreen DIMM labels

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.9.2 (2008-07-30) r40613
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Added GPL disclaimer as per new Sun policy

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.9.1 (2008-06-23) r39082
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Fixed CR 6717586, occasional crash after mce reporting
- Made decoding result to dimm pair explicit
- Warnings fix

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.9 (2008-06-19) r38970
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Fixed decode algorithm for rev.F and rev.10
- Correctly reports 128-bit interface for rev.F and rev.10
- Support for more Quad-Core chips

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.8 (2008-03-12) r34461
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Added --params and --setparam options, for offline operations
- Added force_cpu parameter feature
- Made init scripts remove EDAC kernel module
- Updates to dimm decode algorithms
- Log decode results in syslog

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.7 (2007-08-15) r28257
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Opteron Family 10h (quad core) support

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.6 (2007-05-18) r26075
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Protects against non-root execution
- Better Opteron revision detection
- More debug-mode messages

---------------------------------------------------------------
Herd 1.5 (2007-03-05) r23528
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Added seltest test option
- Removed some compile warnings
- Switched node,dimm info in ipmi message

